    #pragma PROPERTY ColorSynchronizationModeOnSubElements
  /**
   * Returns or sets the "ColorSynchronizationModeOnSubElements" parameter.
   * <br/><b>Role:</b> This parameter determines color synchronization mode for imported features in a part.
   * <br/>Color synchronization mode OnSubElements defines whether the imported feature, created through copy/paste as result with link mechanism, copies reference
   * feature colors on his overloaded faces or not. If it is valuated to 1, synchronization will be effective and reference subelements colors will be reported. 
   * If it is defined to 0, nothing will be copied(default mode).
   * @param oActivated
   *   Current "ColorSynchronizationModeOnSubElements" parameter's value:
   *      <ul><li>TRUE or 1 if reference subelements colors are reported on imported feature,</li>
   *      <li>FALSE or 0 otherwise.</li></ul>
